<li>Tweed, Anne, NSTA President, 2004. Direct Instruction: Is It the Most Effective Science Teaching Strategy?, NSTA Web News Digest, 12/15/2004.</li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li>Rebar, M. (2007). Academic acceleration in first grade using the Direct Instruction model. (Report No. 2007-1). Cheney, WA: Eastern Washington University.</li>
</ul>
<p>Available for download at: <a href="http://www.ewu.edu/getset/Academic_Acceleration_G1_TR_2007-1.pdf" class="external free" title="http://www.ewu.edu/getset/Academic_Acceleration_G1_TR_2007-1.pdf" rel="nofollow">http://www.ewu.edu/getset/Academic_Acceleration_G1_TR_2007-1.pdf</a></p>
